{{Top|leg}}
'''Brachno-jags''' were small carnivores, a hundred of which could strip the flesh off a [[Human/Legends|Human]] in five or six hours. They were used to perform very painful [[Torture/Legends|torture]] and executions, and were mostly used on backwater and [[Outer Rim Territories/Legends|outer-rim]] worlds.

